<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.998422>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Taphura lanceola n. sp.: A, holotype male habitus; B, holotype male dorsum; C, holotype male timbal cover; D, paratype male operculum; E, holotype male lateral view of genitalia; F, holotype male posterior view of genitalia. Scale bar: A, 2 cm; B, 2 mm; C, 0.5 mm; D – F, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/998422/files/figure.png" ;
